Hi [~arpitagarwal].  This looks good.  I just have one suggestion: consider refactoring the common logic of {{addTerseLoggingExceptions}} and {{addSuppressedLoggingExceptions}}.  Then, those two methods could reduce to one-liners, like:

{{terseExceptions = addExceptions(terseExceptions, exceptionClass);}}

{{suppressedExceptions = addExceptions(suppressedExceptions, exceptionClass);}}
